</P>
<P>
   He worked briefly for one of the country's best-known reformers,
Anatoly Sobchak. But his successful career in the FSB (as the KGB
is now known) suggests that liberalism is not always his prime
concern.
</P>
<P>
   Only on one issue can we see just where Putin stands. Very
