blame the whole thing on going out for chowder with Arthur. He got
to droning on about some client of his and pretty soon my focus
wandered. Suddenly, there I was in a purple Cadillac. (Schuett, Cox
News Service) MOVED
</P>
<P>
   KABAT-COLUMN _ WACO, Texas _ As I have grown older, though,
there are many more things that I don't see clearly: newspapers and
telephone directories as well as right and wrong, truth and
untruth. A lot of lines are blurring for me and bifocals are
addressing only a few of them. (Kabat, Waco Tribune-Herald) MOVED
</P>
<P>
   YOUNG-COLUMN _ WACO, Texas _ Until we as a nation come to a
grips with the excesses of campaign finance, here's what we do with
some of the excess: No more taxpayer-financed security for
office-holders running for president. Pay your own way, boys.
</P>
<P>
   (Young, Waco Tribune-Herald) MOVED
</P>
